## Disclaimer

This cryptographic system is provided for educational and research purposes. 
While the system implements advanced security mechanisms:

- This software has not undergone formal security audits
- Use in production environments is at your own risk
- The authors assume no liability for data breaches or security incidents
- Users are responsible for compliance with local regulations regarding cryptographic software

For production deployments involving sensitive data, professional security 
audits and legal compliance reviews are strongly recommended.

